		</p>
		
		
	
																	
								
																							
								
				
						<div class="event-date">Tue., December 05, 20:00 – </div>
				
		
		
										
		<h2 class="article-ttl">
			Artist Talk: Antti Tenetz - Getting lost between Spaces
		</h2>
	</a>
	
																									<div class="tag-btn"><a href="http://bioclub.org/en/tags/イベント">#イベント</a></div>
		
							<div class="thumb">
				<a href="http://bioclub.org/en/event/antti-tenetz-getting-lost" class="ct-block hv-op">
					<span class="img-wrapper"><img src="http://bioclub.org/assets/images/Antti2.jpg" alt="Artist Talk: Antti Tenetz - Getting lost between Spaces"></span>
					
																<p class="ct-link-lead">​What can other than human life, slime molds, local and AI machine systems based knowledge and cowandering teach us about survival and evolving as whole.<br />
<br />
人間の生命、粘菌、ローカルおよびAI機械システムに基づく知識、そして臆病さ以外に、生存と全体としての進化について何を教えてくれるのだろうか。</p>
